  {"slug":"exponential-moving-average","title":"Exponential Moving Average","description":"## EMA\n\nImplement EMA. `alpha = 2/(span+1)`. EMA[0]=prices[0].","difficulty":"easy","category":"statistics","starter_code":"def ema(prices: list, span: int) -> list:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"def ema(prices,span):\n    a=2/(span+1); r=[prices[0]]\n    for p in prices[1:]: r.append(p*a+r[-1]*(1-a))\n    return r\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"prices":[10.0,20.0,30.0],"span":2},"expected":[10.0,16.666666666666668,24.444444444444443]},{"input":{"prices":[1.0,1.0,1.0],"span":2},"expected":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}],"function":"ema"},"tags":["ema","statistics"],"points":75},

  {"slug":"rolling-zscore","title":"Rolling Z-Score","description":"## Rolling Z-Score\n\nCompute rolling z-score with population std (ddof=0). Return `None` for warm-up.","difficulty":"easy","category":"statistics","starter_code":"def rolling_zscore(prices: list, window: int) -> list:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"def rolling_zscore(prices,window):\n    r=[]\n    for i in range(len(prices)):\n        if i<window-1: r.append(None); continue\n        w=prices[i-window+1:i+1]; m=sum(w)/window\n        s=(sum((x-m)**2 for x in w)/window)**0.5\n        r.append(0.0 if s==0 else (prices[i]-m)/s)\n    return r\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"prices":[10,20,30,40,50],"window":3},"expected":[None,None,0.0,0.0,0.0]},{"input":{"prices":[10,10,10],"window":2},"expected":[None,0.0,0.0]}],"function":"rolling_zscore"},"tags":["zscore","normalization"],"points":75},

  {"slug":"sharpe-ratio","title":"Sharpe Ratio","description":"## Sharpe Ratio\n\nAnnualized Sharpe = `(mean(r) - rf/252) / std(r) * sqrt(252)`. Use ddof=1. Return 0.0 if std==0.","difficulty":"easy","category":"statistics","starter_code":"def sharpe_ratio(returns: list, risk_free_rate: float = 0.02) -> float:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"import math\ndef sharpe_ratio(returns,risk_free_rate=0.02):\n    n=len(returns); m=sum(returns)/n\n    v=sum((r-m)**2 for r in returns)/(n-1) if n>1 else 0\n    s=v**0.5\n    return 0.0 if s==0 else (m-risk_free_rate/252)/s*252**0.5\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"returns":[0.0]*10,"risk_free_rate":0.0},"expected":0.0},{"input":{"returns":[0.001]*252,"risk_free_rate":0.0},"expected":0.0}],"function":"sharpe_ratio"},"tags":["sharpe","risk","performance"],"points":100},

  {"slug":"max-drawdown","title":"Maximum Drawdown","description":"## Max Drawdown\n\nReturn maximum drawdown as negative float. `DD(t) = (peak - value) / peak`.","difficulty":"medium","category":"statistics","starter_code":"def max_drawdown(equity_curve: list) -> float:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"def max_drawdown(equity_curve):\n    peak=equity_curve[0]; mdd=0.0\n    for v in equity_curve:\n        if v>peak: peak=v\n        dd=(v-peak)/peak\n        if dd<mdd: mdd=dd\n    return mdd\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"equity_curve":[100,110,105,95,120]},"expected":round((95-110)/110,6)},{"input":{"equity_curve":[100,100,100]},"expected":0.0},{"input":{"equity_curve":[100,50,25]},"expected":-0.75}],"function":"max_drawdown"},"tags":["drawdown","risk"],"points":100},

  {"slug":"rolling-beta","title":"Rolling Beta","description":"## Rolling Beta\n\nCompute rolling beta of asset returns vs benchmark returns.\nbeta = Cov(asset,bench) / Var(bench). Return None for warm-up.","difficulty":"medium","category":"statistics","starter_code":"def rolling_beta(asset_returns: list, bench_returns: list, window: int) -> list:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"def rolling_beta(asset_returns,bench_returns,window):\n    r=[]\n    for i in range(len(asset_returns)):\n        if i<window-1: r.append(None); continue\n        a=asset_returns[i-window+1:i+1]; b=bench_returns[i-window+1:i+1]\n        ma=sum(a)/window; mb=sum(b)/window\n        cov=sum((x-ma)*(y-mb) for x,y in zip(a,b))/window\n        vb=sum((y-mb)**2 for y in b)/window\n        r.append(0.0 if vb==0 else cov/vb)\n    return r\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"asset_returns":[0.01,0.02,-0.01,0.03,0.01],"bench_returns":[0.01,0.02,-0.01,0.03,0.01],"window":3},"expected":[None,None,1.0,1.0,1.0]}],"function":"rolling_beta"},"tags":["beta","regression"],"points":125},

