  {"slug":"black-scholes-call","title":"Black-Scholes Call Price","description":"## Black-Scholes Call\n\nImplement the Black-Scholes formula for a European call option.\n\n`C = S*N(d1) - K*exp(-r*T)*N(d2)`\n\nwhere:\n- `d1 = (ln(S/K) + (r + σ²/2)*T) / (σ*√T)`\n- `d2 = d1 - σ*√T`\n- N(x) = standard normal CDF\n\nUse `math.erf` to implement N(x).","difficulty":"medium","category":"options","starter_code":"def bs_call(S: float, K: float, T: float, r: float, sigma: float) -> float:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"import math\ndef bs_call(S,K,T,r,sigma):\n    def N(x): return (1+math.erf(x/math.sqrt(2)))/2\n    d1=(math.log(S/K)+(r+sigma**2/2)*T)/(sigma*T**0.5)\n    d2=d1-sigma*T**0.5\n    return S*N(d1)-K*math.exp(-r*T)*N(d2)\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"S":100.0,"K":100.0,"T":1.0,"r":0.05,"sigma":0.2},"expected":10.4506},{"input":{"S":100.0,"K":110.0,"T":0.5,"r":0.05,"sigma":0.25},"expected":6.0397}],"function":"bs_call"},"tags":["black-scholes","options","pricing"],"points":150},

  {"slug":"black-scholes-put","title":"Black-Scholes Put Price","description":"## Black-Scholes Put\n\nImplement the Black-Scholes formula for a European put option.\n\nUse put-call parity: `P = C - S + K*exp(-r*T)`","difficulty":"medium","category":"options","starter_code":"def bs_put(S: float, K: float, T: float, r: float, sigma: float) -> float:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"import math\ndef bs_put(S,K,T,r,sigma):\n    def N(x): return (1+math.erf(x/math.sqrt(2)))/2\n    d1=(math.log(S/K)+(r+sigma**2/2)*T)/(sigma*T**0.5)\n    d2=d1-sigma*T**0.5\n    return K*math.exp(-r*T)*N(-d2)-S*N(-d1)\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"S":100.0,"K":100.0,"T":1.0,"r":0.05,"sigma":0.2},"expected":5.5735},{"input":{"S":100.0,"K":90.0,"T":1.0,"r":0.05,"sigma":0.2},"expected":1.6265}],"function":"bs_put"},"tags":["black-scholes","put","options"],"points":150},

