  {"slug":"pair-trading-zscore","title":"Pair Trading Z-Score Signal","description":"## Pair Trading\n\nGiven two price series A and B:\n1. Compute spread = A - B\n2. Compute rolling z-score of spread\n3. Return signals: 1 if z < -2, -1 if z > 2, 0 otherwise\n\nReturn None for warm-up period.","difficulty":"medium","category":"strategies","starter_code":"def pair_trading_signal(prices_a: list, prices_b: list, window: int = 20) -> list:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"def pair_trading_signal(prices_a,prices_b,window=20):\n    spread=[a-b for a,b in zip(prices_a,prices_b)]; signals=[]\n    for i in range(len(spread)):\n        if i<window-1: signals.append(None); continue\n        w=spread[i-window+1:i+1]; m=sum(w)/window\n        s=(sum((x-m)**2 for x in w)/window)**0.5\n        z=(spread[i]-m)/s if s>0 else 0\n        signals.append(1 if z<-2 else -1 if z>2 else 0)\n    return signals\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"prices_a":[100.0]*25,"prices_b":[100.0]*25,"window":20},"expected":[None]*19+[0]*6}],"function":"pair_trading_signal"},"tags":["pairs","stat-arb"],"points":150},

  {"slug":"momentum-signal","title":"Momentum Signal","description":"## Momentum Signal\n\nCompute a momentum signal:\n`momentum[i] = (price[i] - price[i - lookback]) / price[i - lookback]`\n\nReturn 1 if momentum > threshold, -1 if < -threshold, else 0. Return None for warm-up.","difficulty":"medium","category":"strategies","starter_code":"def momentum_signal(prices: list, lookback: int = 20, threshold: float = 0.02) -> list:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"def momentum_signal(prices,lookback=20,threshold=0.02):\n    r=[]\n    for i in range(len(prices)):\n        if i<lookback: r.append(None); continue\n        m=(prices[i]-prices[i-lookback])/prices[i-lookback]\n        r.append(1 if m>threshold else -1 if m<-threshold else 0)\n    return r\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"prices":[100]*5+[103]*20,"lookback":5,"threshold":0.02},"expected":[None]*5+[0]+[1]*19}],"function":"momentum_signal"},"tags":["momentum","signal","trend"],"points":125},

  {"slug":"macd-signal","title":"MACD Signal Line","description":"## MACD\n\nMACD = EMA(fast) - EMA(slow)\nSignal = EMA(MACD, signal_period)\nHistogram = MACD - Signal\n\nReturn `(macd, signal, histogram)` as three lists. EMA[0] = value[0].","difficulty":"hard","category":"strategies","starter_code":"def macd(prices: list, fast: int = 12, slow: int = 26, signal_period: int = 9) -> tuple:\n    pass\n","solution_code":"def macd(prices,fast=12,slow=26,signal_period=9):\n    def ema(data,span):\n        a=2/(span+1); r=[data[0]]\n        for x in data[1:]: r.append(x*a+r[-1]*(1-a))\n        return r\n    ef=ema(prices,fast); es=ema(prices,slow)\n    m=[f-s for f,s in zip(ef,es)]\n    sig=ema(m,signal_period)\n    hist=[mv-sv for mv,sv in zip(m,sig)]\n    return (m,sig,hist)\n","test_cases":{"cases":[{"input":{"prices":[float(i) for i in range(1,31)],"fast":3,"slow":5,"signal_period":3},"expected":"__len_check__"}],"function":"macd"},"tags":["macd","ema","technical"],"points":175},

